Annotations
@Entity-used to mark any class as enitity
@Table-used to change table details
@Id-used to mark column as id ... ie primary key
@GeneratedValue-hibernate will automatically generate values for that using an internal sequence, so that we don't require it to set manually
@Column-can be used to psecify column mappings, to change column name in associated table in database
@Transient-tells hibernate not to save this field
@Temporal-tells hibernate the format in which date has to be saved
@Lob-tells hibernate that it is large object, not simple object

@OneToOne @OneToMany @MAnyToOne @JoinColumn
